OL,6,FLike all shop owners, Parvez Akhtar
OL,7,Ftakes measures to protect his stock in
OL,8,FMiddlesbrough.
OL,10,FBut the barbed wire he showed us at
OL,11,Fhis mobile repairs store is also there
OL,12,Fto protect his family.
OL,14,FNever before has he feared so much for
OL,15,Ftheir safety after a mob of rioters
OL,16,Fcame knocking on his street, and
OL,17,Fworse, last month.
OL,19,F"One guy got a hammer and smashed my
OL,20,Fdoor window and my main window," he
OL,21,Ftold us.
