OL,6,FNew data shared with us shows the
OL,7,Fextraordinary rise in far-right
OL,8,Ftraffic on social media.
OL,10,FOn Telegram, activity surged in the 48
OL,11,Fhours after the Southport attack, in
OL,12,Fwhich three young girls were killed.
OL,14,FThe volume of messages in extremist
OL,15,Fgroups shot up by 87%. And in the
OL,16,Ffollowing days, the momentum only
OL,17,Fbuilt.
OL,19,FBy day ten, far-right activity on
OL,20,FTelegram had surged by 327%.
