OL,6,FFor several years, there have been
OL,7,Fwarnings about the rise of far right
OL,8,Fextremism, which we encountered at ITV
OL,9,FNews in 2021 when we were allowed to
OL,10,Ffilm on the terrorist wings of two
OL,11,Fprisons.
OL,13,FAnd yet some believe the police have
OL,14,Fnot taken the threat seriously enough.
